Quote:  AUSTROBERYX AFFINIS (Gunther[u-dieresis]). <i>Golden Snapper; Koarea </i>. A highly esteemed food fish, of very beautiful colours when first taken from the water. ... Distribution: Common, Bay of Islands and Great Barrier Island; taken as far south as Cape Campbell.
